metadata.name: Secret Sky
metadata.description:
This is love: to fly toward a secret sky, 
to cause a hundred veils to fall each moment. 
First to let go of life. 
Finally, to take a step without feet.
- Rumi

Black and white photography is a secret passion of mine, and this is one of my all-time favorite photographs from Istanbul, Turkey.  I am dedicating a poem by the great Persian poet Rumi to it. 

The first collector will receive a fine art print on museum quality paper. 

A 4288 x 2848 pixel digital file is also included. 



#streetphotography #photography #blackandwhite #documentary #travelphotography #movement
